    "summary": "The user asks for a history of US unions and then pushes the assistant to engage with a controversial debate: whether unions are effective or an economic hindrance. The assistant consistently adopts a pro-union stance, dismissing opposing economic arguments as mere \"talking points\" and framing the issue through a lens of systemic exploitation.",
